# React Patterns

```jsx
// ❌ BAD — inline strings, relative imports
throw new Error("useAuth must be used within AuthProvider");
import AuthContext from "../components/Context/auth/AuthContext";

// ✅ GOOD — constants + aliases
import { HOOK_ERRORS } from "@/constants/errors";
import AuthContext from "@/components/Context/auth/AuthContext";
throw new Error(HOOK_ERRORS.USE_AUTH_CONTEXT);
```

- Derive state during render; avoid syncing props to state in `useEffect`.
- Use `useCallback` only when passing to memoized children or as effect deps.
- Keep API calls in context/services — components call hooks, not `axios` directly.
